-->> Docker is a container management service.
-->> Easily develop applications, ship them into containers and then deploy anywhere.
-->> We can run it anywhere means physical machine or virtual machine even on cloud also.
-->> Docker Hub is a registry service on the cloud.
-->> Downlod the docker images from docker hub that are build by you or others.
-->> Can also upload docker images into docker hub.
-->> Docker image is a combination of a file system and parameters.	

